quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,48,"Gomɗii ɓe ɗaɓɓiino fitina on ko adii, ɓe waylitan-maa fiyaaku on haa goonga kan ari, fiyaaku Alla on feeñi tawi ko ɓe añuɓe (ɗum)"
  9,49,"Hino e maɓɓe wi'oowo : \"Duŋano(sakkitan) lam (heddagol), wata a fitinam.\" Anndee ko e fitina on (tigiri) ɓe yani; pellet, Jahannama ko huuɓitaynge(fiiltii) heeferɓe ɓen"
  9,50,"Si moƴƴere heɓii ma, metta ɓe. Si musiiba heɓii ma, ɓe wi'a : \"Banni men nanngunoo fiyaaku amen ko adii.\" Hiɓe huccita ko ɓe weltiiɓe"
  9,51,"Maaku : \"Heɓataa men si wanaa kon ko Alla winndani men. Ko Kanko woni Giɗo amen. Ko e Alla woni ko gomɗimɓe ɓen fawotoo"
  9,52,"Maaku : \"Hara hiɗon habbitori men si wanaa gootel e moƴƴereeji ɗin ɗiɗi? Menen kadi meɗen faditii e mon, nde Alla meminirta on lepte immorde ka Makko, maa e juuɗe amen. Habbitee! Menen meɗen habbodi e mooɗon"
  9,53,"Maaku : \"Wintee(nafqe) hiɗon yiɗi maa hiɗon añi : on jaɓantaake, onon on laatinoke yimɓe faasiqiiɓe"
  9,54,"Haɗaali ɓe jaɓeede wintaaje maɓɓe ɗen, si wanaa ko ɓe yeddiri kon Alla e Nulaaɗo Makko on, ɓe arataa e julde si wanaa hara ko ɓe aamuɓe, ɓe wintotaako si wanaa hara ko ɓe añuɓe"